      • train

        public void train(PatternSet set,
                  int epochs)
        Trains the SOM depending on the 'supervised' flag. If not supervised, a basic SOM training is conducted. If supervised, the basic OLVQ1 algorithm is used assigning specific neurons to specific clusters.
        Parameters:
        set - the complete training set
        epochs - the number of epochs
